Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.97,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.20,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:54.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:58.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.07,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:15.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:30.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.99,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:40.44,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:44.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:48.18,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:51.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.66,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:58.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:03.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:54.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}隨心所欲地去描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.02,0:00:58.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描繪的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}萬里無雲的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:11.07,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邊無際的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:15.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}純潔無瑕的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:18.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈著無限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:22.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於能自由翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.65,0:01:25.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}長出了美麗的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.22,0:01:30.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無瑕的瞳孔在尋求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:33.99,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:37.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那無數的願望中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.27,0:01:40.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一個能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:44.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:48.18,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要緊緊抓住那夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.19,0:01:51.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童時的那個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:58.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描寫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:03.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.50,0:23:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}禁忌的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:43.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:49.96,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:58.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:06.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:15.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:23.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:31.05,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:39.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:47.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:55.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:43.30,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:49.96,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.96,0:21:58.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:06.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:15.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.81,0:22:23.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:31.05,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.16,0:22:39.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.73,0:22:47.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:55.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請饒恕 請饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我一個人的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要責罰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就責罰我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百姓是沒有任何罪過的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.22,0:00:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你背負著內疚這樣苟延殘喘下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發發慈悲… 請發發慈悲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾魯姆伊被毀滅了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加查塔拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的事？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說你就不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余問你為什麼要毀滅艾魯姆伊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:02:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人們已經沒有剩餘的戰鬥力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余應該說過不要向不抵抗的人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的同情只會帶來怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上您不是這樣說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能將一族人不分老幼全部殺掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是為了聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維恩庫亞殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣對聖上說話太不敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我說話的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理 希恩殿下 你也說些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希恩殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聖上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維恩庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的不滿余知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下令不嚴余也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就不追究了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝聖上的寬恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:03:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 希恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不正是利用聖上的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將全大陸統一的大好時機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統一？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定總有一天 還會出現這樣的鼠輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要利用聖上的力量將全大陸統一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出一個沒有紛爭的真正的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會說些有用處的話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實也應該讓大家知道支配全大陸的到底是該哪個種族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標應該是統一全大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一樣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正全大陸都是在我們夏庫克波爾族的統治下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統一全大陸的國民和支配他們是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統一和支配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維恩庫亞 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肅靜 現在可是在聖上面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次丸你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然余應該進行全大陸統一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在比起擴大國土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏固民生才是更為重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余的國家根基還沒有穩定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下源次丸是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就照源次丸說的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要穩固國家的根基
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聽到聖上的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.45,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾能陪我小酌一番否
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄到了幾條鮮美的好魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出行嗎 那請讓在下也同行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 繼續吧 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾露露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣勢不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼好的大伙在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs48}還是太嫩了 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努巴尼和哈普拉普向庫涅卡門發起進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾賽謝奇卡的遭遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該讓世人充分瞭解到庫涅卡門的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是以為兩國同時進攻的話還是有勝算的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰果如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門壓倒性的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是向庫涅卡門亮出獠牙的人的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們一定要受到如此的摧殘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我們擁有能夠制壓全大陸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我們寧日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們不用為他族的威脅擔驚受怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠安心生活的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下十分理解大家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在需要鞏固國土
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那時我們都要一直被殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏固了國家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我被殺死的孩子就能夠回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是被「偉大之父」所選擇的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用我們夏庫克波爾族的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓庫涅卡門的威名傳遍大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 又要有戰爭發生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也不是一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在庫涅卡門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不少人大聲呼籲要統一全大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 還是要做好準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願這準備是多餘的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的月亮很美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不這麼覺得嗎 白皇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余喜歡眺望月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像太陽那樣毫不留情的照射大地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮的光芒靜靜地映襯著黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我們溫柔的包裹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「偉大之父」似乎比起太陽也更喜歡月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.16,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想說的話 我不會勉強你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余並沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要任何事都自己一人承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的人這個世界上是沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰都會煩惱 受傷 痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並想要依靠別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要獲得別人的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.31,0:10:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇你也是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾露露嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有艾露露他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而庫婭你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有源次丸和紗雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩惱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以稍微和他們談談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余並不是一個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻下一個村落 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 內壩茨梅？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上想要鞏固國家的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能夠理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況已經不允許這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們這樣做的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵略者正在將我們的人民置於戰火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該是下定決心的時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都希望聖上您統一全大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是保護的話是不能救助人民的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要創造能讓我們安心生活的世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我們自己站上頂峰才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不正擁有實現這一切的力量——阿弗˙卡姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次丸在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著紗雅去查看村莊的狀況了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內壩茨梅攻勢迅猛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽庫哈茲山的村莊已被燒燬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏固了國家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天死去的人民就能夠死而復生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余…不能再被你們的話所左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余以自己的意識決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通告全大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余 阿姆魯利涅沃爾卡˙庫婭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始統一全大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門的宣戰公告？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總大將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏固北部邊境的守備 東霞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈克奧羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧 死吧 大家都去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（庫涅卡門萬歲——）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（庫涅卡門的榮耀——）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付大神教會？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教會他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是一些敬奉禍日神的低賤的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會和他們發生戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁早擊潰他們不是更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解放者」是人民的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻大神教會的話就意味著和所有的人民為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與全民為敵的話 你打算要使我們孤立無援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就是被孤立了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要和我們夏庫克波爾族共同生存的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希恩 哈維恩庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天出擊 去準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上已經忘記了那位大人的溫暖了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上正在逐漸失去那份溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再一次得到手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這是用力量能夠奪取的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.09,0:15:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都下達了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就已經無法阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.49,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門對父親大人的國家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被身為主君的宿命所翻弄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印吾等主人之名為常世之牢獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印吾等主人之名為常世之牢獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印吾等主人之名為常世之牢獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.61,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大封印」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有這樣的招數…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏庫克波爾族   深受「偉大之父」所愛護…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…並因此而受到迫害的民眾們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就借由大神「解放者」之手讓你們安息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.63,0:17:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「大封印」被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德伊 你還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你也不可能做到這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教會的制壓已經完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈維恩庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把圖斯克爾的王——白皇帶到余的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹記尊命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.19,0:18:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教會陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賢大僧正 生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙特 召集阿闍梨位的上師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結 父親大人一定還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們要相信這點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:18:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們還有不得不代替父親大人去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結也會幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神結也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.26,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門越過了國境進入了圖斯克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侯盍羅城被突破 守軍被全部殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東霞和克羅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人正一邊牽制敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊向此處撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.07,0:19:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 朧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫涅卡門的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗只會增加犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兄長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都城…放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據現在的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最好的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露 引導人民避難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哈克奧羅你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量拖延他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 聖上也請一起避難
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝納威
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是聖上您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白皇大人您沒事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定可以重整大局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就請交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為您的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您接受我們的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是並不是就這麼結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 一定要活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 庫涅卡門的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不會無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來圖斯克爾也都是一群笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑生銹的刀槍和脆軟的弓箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想阻止我們的阿弗˙卡姆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的是為避難拖延時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請不要做有勇無謀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了


